{"tid":713346,"cid":6,"subCid":0,"title":"亞軍停算唔算係攞嚟賤？","createTime":"2018-06-22T17:20:55.000Z","updateTime":"2018-06-22T17:36:24.000Z","uid":5290,"like":7,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":2,"replies":[{"pid":"ecd7e5b2482059fcf154c2dc10675abcbd91af81","tid":713346,"uid":5290,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-06-22T17:20:56.000Z","msg":"阿根廷足總日前宣佈，球隊的首席門將沙治奧羅美路因為右膝受傷，將會緣盡今屆世界盃。不過羅美路的太太艾蓮娜在一個阿根廷的清談節目上就爆料，指羅美路的傷勢並不嚴重，可趕及世界盃復出：「羅美路並非韌帶或肌肉斷裂，只是有一塊軟骨鬆了，醫生告訴我們他最多只需要休息二至三星期，可以參加世界盃。」<br />\n<br />\n艾蓮娜又指，羅美路今次無法參加世界盃其實另有內情：「球隊內有很多人都想把他趕走，足總說他韌帶斷裂只是想息事寧人，但我已經厭倦他們的慌話。我不知道出說這些話的人到底是無能、不知情抑或懦弱，但說他因傷退隊根本是個爛理由。」<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://hk.sports.appledaily.com/sports/realtime/article/20180524/58233231\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.sports.appledaily.com%2Fsports%2Frealtime%2Farticle%2F20180524%2F58233231&d=gHWey0NjhuctaFPpesYHTU4boqMkoHyMuoHHSR1H%2BGk%3D&h=3fb68267\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.sports.appledaily.com%2Fsports%2Frealtime%2Farticle%2F20180524%2F58233231&h=ea20e359\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://hk.sports.appledaily.com/sports/realtime/article/20180524/58233231</a><br />\n<br />\n用卡巴尼路<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n抵啦<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"65247ad79ba731e491e3e4db26117198b996a97d","tid":713346,"uid":5290,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-06-22T17:24:22.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/no.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"0f9341bac5d5cdede3db4c9603bb812d453a3a8d","tid":713346,"uid":29080,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-06-22T17:33:00.000Z","msg":"真"},{"pid":"4a247723d7f5cee6e66607795ee2b2cef4fe455c","tid":713346,"uid":5290,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-06-22T17:36:24.000Z","msg":"安美路力場<img src=\"/assets/faces/fifa/slick.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n咬住香口膠守龍"}]}